<h2>anonymous vs use-credentials</h2>
<p>Almost all use cases call for <code>anonymous</code>. Use <code>use-credentials</code> only when the server requires authentication (cookies, client certificates) to serve the resource and is configured to accept credentialed CORS requests.</p>

